# terra-siege radar booster — extends radar range while alive.
# Tower + foundation. Rotating dish + tip pip stay procedural (animated yaw).
# Local frame: +Z forward. c21 tower + foundation.
o radar_booster

# Foundation 2.6 × 0.6 × 2.6 at (0, 0.1, 0)
v -1.3 -0.2 -1.3
v  1.3 -0.2 -1.3
v  1.3  0.4 -1.3
v -1.3  0.4 -1.3
v -1.3 -0.2  1.3
v  1.3 -0.2  1.3
v  1.3  0.4  1.3
v -1.3  0.4  1.3

# Tower 1.6 × 3.6 × 1.6 at (0, 1.8, 0)
v -0.8  0.0 -0.8
v  0.8  0.0 -0.8
v  0.8  3.6 -0.8
v -0.8  3.6 -0.8
v -0.8  0.0  0.8
v  0.8  0.0  0.8
v  0.8  3.6  0.8
v -0.8  3.6  0.8

usemtl c21
g foundation
